I recently had the green wire from the coil to the dizzy come loose, 
livening up my freeway commute a little.

Always rule out the easiest/cheapest solutions before you go replacing 
anything. Make sure all wires are whole, connected and getting a good 
ground. Also that your battery terminals have a good connection.

